reviews.review_text: Good show next night much better remember think this was pretty solid when we saw it and good help slip frank  but the next night was the macdaddy of the tour
Best sounding source I like the sound on this source the best out of the bunch.  As of 2021, I would say the nak 100 Hill source is the best sounding Source.  This is now my 2nd fav source.
